      Constructor for building an appointment.
      Parameters:
      apptID - The id of the appointment.
      apptTitle - The title of the appointment.
      apptDescription - The description of the appointment.
      apptLocation - The location of the appointment.
      contactID - The contact id for the appointment.
      apptType - The type of appointment.
      Start - The start time and date of the appointment.
      End - The end time and date of the appointment.
      customerID - The customerID for the appointment.
      userID - The userID for with the appointment.
